p: Dan Yang and Xuee Chen are joint the first authors. The study conceptualization was done by Jun Yin and Zhihui Liu. Isolation and purification of compounds were conducted by Xuee Chen and Xida Liu. The data analysis was done by Dan Yang, Janxiu Zhai, and Sikai Li. Dan Yang and Xuee Chen wrote and prepared the original draft. Zhihui Liu, Jun Yin, and Na Han wrote, reviewed, and edited the manuscript. All authors have read and agreed to the published version of the manuscript.
